WEBVTT

00:00:02.259 --> 00:00:11.630
At the tender age, I have a troubled mind, as to how I will be pleasing to God and also

00:00:11.630 --> 00:00:18.210
at the same time be pleasing in the eyes of the voodoo.

00:00:18.210 --> 00:00:22.890
Two of my siblings died before I was born.

00:00:22.890 --> 00:00:33.600
So my mother was seeking protection, all through her pregnancy, with me, my mother was

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:42.960
made to believe that when she goes to the voodoo shrine regularly, she will be protected

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:44.759
from the witches.

00:00:44.759 --> 00:00:53.119
This means she has to walk about four miles to the shrine regularly barefooted.

00:00:53.119 --> 00:01:01.520
After my bed, I was sent to the voodoo shrine to be protected from the attack of the witches.

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:04.359
I was kept there.

00:01:04.359 --> 00:01:11.400
I got baptized into the cardiac church, there we were taught that those who worshipped

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:17.519
idols, the voodoos, will be bent in an everlasting hellfire.

00:01:17.519 --> 00:01:19.920
I was terrified.

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:28.760
One day I asked my father, wouldn't the priest be angry if he knows that we, after going

00:01:28.760 --> 00:01:33.840
for the communion, still go into the shrine?

00:01:33.840 --> 00:01:43.680
My father came back with the news that the priest said, I can still go ahead being an idol

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:48.519
worshiper and at the same time being a Catholic.

00:01:48.519 --> 00:02:01.379
I became disturbed, I became confused, I came across Jehovah's Witnesses, when I was

00:02:01.379 --> 00:02:04.859
of age and left the village.

00:02:04.859 --> 00:02:13.400
I bombarded them with questions, so I demanded a book.

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:21.360
I read the book before they break, so that night, in my heart, I broke away from the voodoo

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:29.009
ship and also from the Catholic religion.

00:02:29.009 --> 00:02:34.090
I was afraid to confront my father over the issue.

00:02:34.090 --> 00:02:45.110
In our culture, it's not easy for a young man to take such a crucial decision.

00:02:45.110 --> 00:02:50.789
Before I could be aware, there was the news in the village, but now, don't go has joined

00:02:50.789 --> 00:02:58.430
the new religion, so anytime I go home, relatives will knock on my door, I don't, to advise

00:02:58.430 --> 00:03:03.069
me to retain my decision.

00:03:03.069 --> 00:03:21.539
My worry was how to inform my father, and one day, my father invited me and then inquired

00:03:21.539 --> 00:03:30.539
of me of what was really happening, and it became a very strong confrontation.

00:03:30.539 --> 00:03:42.189
I told him, I'll worship Jehovah, Jehovah is the only God I'll worship.

00:03:42.189 --> 00:03:49.030
So he fled up, left me and then went into this room, so I also entered my room and started

00:03:49.030 --> 00:03:50.030
singing.

00:03:50.030 --> 00:03:59.620
Once with confusion, our side has waived, drinking the Catholic religion distilled.

00:03:59.620 --> 00:04:07.500
I was singing so vigorously, I see somebody who has been liberated, because I first, initially,

00:04:07.500 --> 00:04:14.669
I was in prison, but now I am a freed man.

00:04:14.669 --> 00:04:29.199
So since then, I've been saving Jehovah, the fear of man has been overcome.

00:04:29.199 --> 00:04:35.480
I am no longer a captive of the fear of death, or even the dead.

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:43.519
I no longer engage myself in any practices that are contrary to Bible standards.

00:04:43.519 --> 00:04:45.480
I feel liberated.

00:04:50.139 --> 00:04:59.860
It makes me happy when I see my children also saving their only true God, Jehovah, and now

00:04:59.860 --> 00:05:02.459
I live a very happy family life.
